imdb.plot outline: Olga is a Russian v-logger and "aspiring celebrity" who pursues her idea of the American Dream, based entirely on what she sees on her favorite TV show: The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. Her quest for true love and fame in Hollywood is chronicled in her self-directed video diary. Inevitable culture clash, entwined with dramatic "twenty-something" life questions bring chaos and hilarity.
